解", "review": 0, "author": "山下智博", "mid": 1643718, "created": 1766484000, "length": "28:13", "video_review": 419, "aid": 115747170813406, "bvid": "BV1XCqfBmESu", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 1, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16793984, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 667, "typeid": 254, "play": 311192, "pic": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/bd5449287a8e96c3c5b7dd4de42efc7fa6628af2.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "中国年轻人常说“内卷”，\n但日本真的没有在卷吗？\n\n这次，山下智博从中国年轻人的视角出发，\n（我的理解有错误的话请指摘一下！我去重新学习！）\n讲述“内卷、躺平、上岸”这些在中国早已司空见惯的现象。\n而日本作家·麻布竞马场，\n则从日本社会与年轻人的变化谈起，\n回应“日本的内卷到底卷在哪”。\n\n本以为是中日差异，\n聊到最后却发现——\n两国年轻人，正在为几乎同样的问题烦恼。\n\n这也许就是，\n现在这个时代最真实的中日对话。", "copyright": "1", "title": "聊到中国的“卷”，日本作家直接沉默了【中日文化对比】", "review": 0, "author": "山下智博", "mid": 1643718, "created": 1766224800, "length": "23:50", "video_review": 767, "aid": 115746784937207, "bvid": "BV1ycBFBKEQG", "hide_click": false, "is_pay": 0, "is_union_video": 1, "is_steins_gate": 0, "is_live_playback": 0, "is_lesson_video": 0, "is_lesson_finished": 0, "lesson_update_info": "", "jump_url": "", "meta": null, "is_avoided": 0, "season_id": 0, "attribute": 16793984, "is_charging_arc": false, "elec_arc_type": 0, "elec_arc_badge": "", "vt": 0, "enable_vt": 0, "vt_display": "", "playback_position": 0, "is_self_view": false, "view_self_type": 0}, {"comment": 3485, "typeid": 254, "play": 743458, "pic": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/74304c487c94b9714d2a4677af0f8f7eda0e5d07.jpg", "subtitle": "", "description": "哈哈哈哈哈！没想到吧！！！\n现在我没办法继续现在的工作。。。！\n希望大家没有大影响！！！！", "copyright": "3", "title": "我快要不太行了...所以做一个新挑战！", "review": 0, "author": "山下智博", "mid": 1643718, "created": 1765684800, "length": "05:3